nodes.text: The Hidden Enemy, Part 1 is the eighty-first issue in the Star Wars: Republic series of comic books. It was published on January 4, 2006 by Dark Horse Comics.
The first issue of a three-part story that begins during the events of Revenge of the Sith, and reveals a battle that was not shown in that film!

The Separatist attack on the Wookiee homeworld of Kashyyyk demands a strong response from the Republic, and Jedi Masters Luminara Unduli and Quinlan Vos arrive with their clone armies. But there may be more behind the Separatist attack—and more to the Wookiee's defenses than the Jedi know.
Old friends, new enemies, and lots of action!
